### Lista parkingów
GET http://localhost:80/api/admin/parking-lots

### Dodaj parking
POST http://localhost:80/api/admin/parking-lots
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Parking Testowy",
  "address": "ul. Testowa 1, Kraków",
  "zone": "ZONE_A",
  "latitude": 50.0600,
  "longitude": 19.9400,
  "totalSpots": 100,
  "parkingType": "PUBLIC"
}

### Wyszukaj parkingi w promieniu 3 km od Rynku
GET http://localhost:80/api/parking-lots/search?lat=50.0615&lng=19.9370&radiusKm=3&fuelType=DIESEL&emissionStandard=EURO_5

### Sprawdź czy pojazd może wjechać
POST http://localhost:80/api/vehicles/check
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fuelType": "DIESEL",
  "emissionStandard": "EURO_3",
  "zone": "ZONE_A"
}

### Oblicz opłatę za 2h parkowania
GET http://localhost:80/api/parking-fee/calculate?parkingLotId=1&durationMinutes=120
